  [4]: https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/17/docs/api/java.base/java/util/Map.html#unmodifiable
  [5]: https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/17/docs/api/java.base/java/util/List.html#of(E,E,E,E,E)
